OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FA dry morning with bright or
OL,6,Fsunny spells. Bright spells continuing
OL,7,Fthrough the afternoon with showers
OL,8,Fdeveloping, especially in the west
OL,9,Fwhere they may be heavy. Windy at
OL,10,Ftimes.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FCloudy
OL,13,Fand breezy on Saturday with heavy
OL,14,Fshowers clearing later in the day. Dry
OL,15,FSunday and Monday with sunny spells,
OL,16,Fbut possibly cloudier towards the
OL,17,Fcoasts. Becoming warmer in west.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
